quran[35]{c,v,t}:
  70,1,Usaba yasabye ko ibihano bigomba kuzabaho bisohora
  70,2,(Nyamara ibyo bihano) nta kizabibuza kugera ku bahakanyi
  70,3,"(Bizabageraho ku munsi w’imperuka) biturutse kwa Allah, nyir’amayira azamuka (agana mu ijuru)"
  70,4,"Abamalayika ndetse na Roho (Malayika Jibrilu) bazamuka iwe (Allah) mu gihe cy’umunsi umwe ungana n’imyaka ibihumbi mirongo itanu (ya hano ku isi, abandi batari bo bakoresha muri urwo rugendo)"
  70,5,"Bityo, ihangane (yewe Muhamadi) wifashishije ukwihangana kwiza"
  70,6,Mu by’ukuri bo babona (imperuka) iri kure
  70,7,Nyamara twe tukabona iri hafi
  70,8,Umunsi ikirere kizaba nk’umushongi w’umuringa
  70,9,N’imisozi ikaba nk’ubwoya (bukemurwa ku matungo bukorwamo imyambaro)
  70,10,Kandi nta nshuti izigera ibaza iby’inshuti yayo
  70,11,"N’ubwo bazaba barebana (ndetse bakanamenyana, ariko nta cyo bazamarirana). Kubera ibihano by’uwo munsi, umunyabyaha azifuza gutangaho incungu abana be"
  70,12,"Umugore we, umuvandimwe we"
  70,13,N’umuryango we yahungiragaho (akiri ku isi igihe ahuye n’ibimuteye ubwoba)
  70,14,Ndetse n’abari mu isi bose (azifuza kubatangaho incungu) kugira ngo arokoke
  70,15,Ariko nta cyo bizamumarira! Ahubwo azajya mu muriro ugurumana
  70,16,Uhubuzaho uruhu rw’agahanga
  70,17,Uzaba uhamagara uwo ari we wese wateraga umugongo akanirengagiza (ukuri gukubiye muri Qur’an)
  70,18,Akanakusanya (umutungo) akawuhunika (ntawukoreshe mu nzira ya Allah)
  70,19,Mu by’ukuri umuntu yaremanywe ukutihangana
  70,20,"Iyo ikibi kimugezeho, ariheba cyane"
  70,21,"Naho icyiza cyamugeraho, akaba umunyabugugu cyane"
  70,22,Uretse abakora iswala
  70,23,Ba bandi bahozaho iswala zabo
  70,24,Na ba bandi bagena umugabane uzwi (Zakat) mu mitungo yabo
  70,25,Wagenewe usaba n’uwiyumanganyije (nyamara akeneye ubufasha)
  70,26,Na ba bandi bemera ko umunsi w’ibihembo ari ukuri
  70,27,Na ba bandi batinya ibihano bya Nyagasani wabo
  70,28,Kubera ko mu by’ukuri ibihano bya Nyagasani wabo nta n’umwe wakwizera ko bitamugeraho
  70,29,Na ba bandi barinda ubwambure bwabo (ubusambanyi)
  70,30,Uretse ku bagore babo cyangwa se ku bo bafiteho ububasha (abaja). Mu by’ukuri bo ntibabigayirwa
  70,31,"Ariko abazashaka (kwinezeza) ku batari abo (bavuzwe), rwose abo bazaba batandukiriye"
  70,32,Na ba bandi barinda ibyo baragijwe ndetse bakubahiriza n’amasezerano yabo
  70,33,Na ba bandi batanga ubuhamya bw’ukuri
  70,34,Na ba bandi bahozaho iswala zabo (ku bihe byagenwe)
  70,35,Abo bazajya mu busitani (Ijuru) kandi bubashywe